Ramsey Realty Group - Lake Cypress Springs

data.description: 4 bedroom, 2-1/2 bath A-frame style home on just under 20 acres with 2x6 exterior walls, spray foam insulation, and Hardie-board exterior. Galvalume metal roof.  There is a loft above the kitchen with a spiral staircase that can be used as a game room or 5th bedroom. Tile throughout the great room, kitchen, bathrooms, and master suite. The great room has 24-foot ceilings. Large, newly remodeled front porch and huge back deck that overlooks a 2-acre spring-fed stocked pond. This property has several outbuildings. The acreage is fenced and crossed fenced, and the pastures are full of Bahia grass. There's also a RV hookup. The house is on a well and it has a new water pump. There are 2 AC units, and the stove is gas.
